Orientationchangeadvanced_iframe = window.setTimeout(\"recalculateIframeadvanced_iframe()\",100);\n            }, false);\n          }\n        }\n        aiReadyCallbacks.push(initResponsiveIframeadvanced_iframe);</script><style>#advanced_iframe {width: 1px !important;min-width:100% !important;max-width:100% !important;}</style><script type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n<hr />\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\n<blockquote><p>CONTENTS</p>\n<p>Havdallah</p>\n<p>Candle Lighting for Ḥanukkah</p>\n<p><u>Ḥanukkah Songs:</u><br />\n1. Maʿoz Tsur\t<span class=\"hebrew\">מעוז צור</span><br />\n2. Uvaʾu Zarim\t<span class=\"hebrew\">ובאו זרים</span><br />\n3. Avi Hidliḳ\t<span class=\"hebrew\">אבי הדליק</span><br />\n4. Banu Ḥoshekh\t<span class=\"hebrew\">באנו חושך</span><br />\n5. Hava Narima\t<span class=\"hebrew\">הבה נרימה</span><br />\n6. Ḥanukkah, Ḥanukkah\t<span class=\"hebrew\">חנוכה, חנוכה</span><br />\n7. Yᵉmé haḤanukkah\t<span class=\"hebrew\">ימי החנוכה</span><br />\n8. Chanukeh oy Chanukeh\t<span class=\"hebrew\">חנוכה אוי חנוכה</span><br />\n9. Kad ḳatan\t<span class=\"hebrew\">כד קטן</span><br />\n10. Mi Yᵉmalel\t<span class=\"hebrew\">מי ימלל</span><br />\n11. Ner Li\t<span class=\"hebrew\">נר לי</span><br />\n12. Sᵉvivon sov\t<span class=\"hebrew\">סביבון סוב סוב סוב</span><br />\n13. ʿAl Hanisim\t<span class=\"hebrew\">על הנסים</span><br />\n14. Ḳemaḥ Ḳemaḥ\t<span class=\"hebrew\">קמח קמח</span><br />\n15. I Have a Little Dreidel<br />\n16. Light One Candle<br />\n17. <a href=\"/?p=49029\">Ḥanukkah in Santa Monica</a> (Tom Lehrer)</p>\n<p>Blessing after Meal\t<span class=\"hebrew\">ברכת המזון</span><br />\nBlessings after Food\t<span class=\"hebrew\">ברכה אחרונה</span></p>\n<p><u>Other Songs:</u><br />\nAround the World<br />\nHow Long Has This Been Going On?<br />\nSummertime<br />\nThese Foolish Things Remind Me of You<br />\nMy Funny Valentine</p></blockquote>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
